name: Teen Superhero - Titans Squad Version
description:
Teen Superhero - Titans Squad Version is a FREE and fun adventure game!

Entertaining gameplay, hours of fun guaranteed!

Tap to Jump, double tap for double jump - make the teen superhero fly!

Get as far as possible and collect coins - that will give extra points to be on the top of the leaderboard! Invite friends to play for double fun!

Help the titans squad member to jump with just an easy touch.

Teen Superhero - Titans Squad Version is waiting for you - download now and share with friends!
